    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@JanPetr Depends on whether deselecting the refinement yields new results or not. If it does, then the available refinements will appear in its stead. Otherwise, the widget will disappear. In both cases, the previously selected refinement will disappear.\n",
